[
  {
    "startTime": 0.089,
    "endTime": 3.799,
    "text": "Hello, guys.\r\nWelcome to this English course on adjectives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.799,
    "endTime": 11.64,
    "text": "In today's video, I'm going to talk about\r\nprefixes and suffixes that are commonly added"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.64,
    "endTime": 14.600000000000001,
    "text": "to adjectives in English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.6,
    "endTime": 19.509999999999998,
    "text": "A prefix is a few letters added to a beginning"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.51,
    "endTime": 23.48,
    "text": "of a word to change the meaning of that word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.48,
    "endTime": 27.039,
    "text": "And a suffix is a few letters added to the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.039,
    "endTime": 30.62,
    "text": "end of the word to change the meaning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.62,
    "endTime": 32.22,
    "text": "We'll get more into detail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.22,
    "endTime": 33.92,
    "text": "Let's get started."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.44,
    "endTime": 38.98,
    "text": "Let's take a look at a few adjectives with"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.98,
    "endTime": 43.919999999999995,
    "text": "prefixes.\r\nAgain a 'prefix' is a few letters added"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.92,
    "endTime": 48.32,
    "text": "to the beginning of the adjective.\r\nMostly to make it negative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.32,
    "endTime": 52.58,
    "text": "Let's take a look at a few examples."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.58,
    "endTime": 57.72,
    "text": "First we have the prefix 'un'. U, n."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.72,
    "endTime": 64.0,
    "text": "For example, if we take the word, 'fair',\r\nand want to make it negative, we can add u"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.0,
    "endTime": 70.49,
    "text": "– n to have the word 'unfair' which\r\nis the opposite of fair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.49,
    "endTime": 74.65899999999999,
    "text": "Same goes for 'happy'.\r\n'unhappy'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.659,
    "endTime": 84.039,
    "text": "'sure' become 'unsure'.\r\nAnother prefix is i –n , 'in'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.039,
    "endTime": 93.09,
    "text": "To make the adjective negative, again,\r\nFor example, 'active' – 'inactive'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.09,
    "endTime": 97.17,
    "text": "'appropriate'\r\n'inappropriate'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.17,
    "endTime": 101.259,
    "text": "'complete'\r\n'incomplete'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.259,
    "endTime": 110.869,
    "text": "The prefix i –r now, 'ir'.\r\nFor example,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.869,
    "endTime": 114.18,
    "text": "'responsible'\r\n'irresponsible'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.18,
    "endTime": 117.5,
    "text": "'regular'\r\n'irregular'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.5,
    "endTime": 120.819,
    "text": "'rational'\r\n'irrational'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.819,
    "endTime": 126.85900000000001,
    "text": "Then we have the prefix i –m, 'im'.\r\nFor example,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.859,
    "endTime": 130.56,
    "text": "'balance'\r\n'imbalance'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.56,
    "endTime": 134.27,
    "text": "'polite'\r\n'impolite'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.27,
    "endTime": 137.98000000000002,
    "text": "'possible'\r\n'impossible'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.98,
    "endTime": 141.79,
    "text": "And finally, the prefix, 'il'.\r\nI – l."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.79,
    "endTime": 148.569,
    "text": "Like, 'legal'\r\n'illegal'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.569,
    "endTime": 153.099,
    "text": "'literate'\r\n'illiterate'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.1,
    "endTime": 157.23999999999998,
    "text": "'logical'\r\n'illogical'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.24,
    "endTime": 163.10000000000002,
    "text": "These are just a few examples, guys.\r\nThere are so many other prefixes in English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.12,
    "endTime": 166.3,
    "text": "But I hope you now have a better understanding.\r\nLet's move on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.3,
    "endTime": 173.56,
    "text": "Let's now talk about suffixes.\r\nIn English, you can add a few letters to a"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.56,
    "endTime": 178.16,
    "text": "noun or a verb to make it into an adjective."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.16,
    "endTime": 180.52,
    "text": "Not necessarily a negative adjective."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.52,
    "endTime": 182.8,
    "text": "It's not like prefixes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.8,
    "endTime": 185.94,
    "text": "There are so many suffixes in English, but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.94,
    "endTime": 190.12,
    "text": "here is a list of very common ones."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.12,
    "endTime": 192.5,
    "text": "We can find a suffix 'able'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.5,
    "endTime": 196.58,
    "text": "Like, 'adorable'.\r\n'comfortable'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.58,
    "endTime": 202.26000000000002,
    "text": "Also the suffix 'en', e – n.\r\nLike, 'broken'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.26,
    "endTime": 204.29999999999998,
    "text": "'golden'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.3,
    "endTime": 205.48000000000002,
    "text": "'ese'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.48,
    "endTime": 209.2,
    "text": "Like, 'Chinese'.\r\n'Japanese'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.2,
    "endTime": 212.16,
    "text": "'ful'\r\nLike, 'wonderful'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.16,
    "endTime": 214.48,
    "text": "'powerful'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.48,
    "endTime": 215.66,
    "text": "'ative'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.66,
    "endTime": 219.84,
    "text": "Like, 'informative'.\r\n'talkative'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.84,
    "endTime": 222.98,
    "text": "'ous'\r\n'dangerous'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.98,
    "endTime": 225.22,
    "text": "'enormous'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.22,
    "endTime": 226.72,
    "text": "Or 'some'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.72,
    "endTime": 230.88,
    "text": "Like, 'awesome'.\r\n'handsome'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.88,
    "endTime": 236.38,
    "text": "Again, these are just a few examples.\r\nThere are so many suffixes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.38,
    "endTime": 241.639,
    "text": "But I hope you now have a good idea of how\r\nto use suffixes in English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 241.639,
    "endTime": 244.0,
    "text": "Let's now move on to practice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.0,
    "endTime": 245.129,
    "text": "Okay, guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.129,
    "endTime": 250.29999999999998,
    "text": "Let's practice finding adjectives in the\r\nfollowing sentences."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.3,
    "endTime": 253.68,
    "text": "And prefixes or suffixes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.68,
    "endTime": 255.62,
    "text": "Let's have a look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.62,
    "endTime": 260.66,
    "text": "“I have an uncomfortable seat.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.66,
    "endTime": 263.44,
    "text": "Now, can you spot the adjective, first?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.44,
    "endTime": 268.02,
    "text": "Of course, the adjective here is 'uncomfortable'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 268.02,
    "endTime": 272.06,
    "text": "Can you see any prefix or suffix?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.06,
    "endTime": 273.68,
    "text": "I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.68,
    "endTime": 277.08,
    "text": "There is a prefix, which is 'un'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.08,
    "endTime": 281.34,
    "text": "And there is a suffix as well.\r\nThe suffix, 'able'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.34,
    "endTime": 285.41999999999996,
    "text": "Okay, so look at how we transformed the word."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.42,
    "endTime": 289.06,
    "text": "The first word was 'comfort' in English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 289.06,
    "endTime": 295.86,
    "text": "First, we added a suffix to make it into an\r\nadjective, which is 'comfortable'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.86,
    "endTime": 301.12,
    "text": "And then we added a prefix, 'un', to make\r\nit negative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.12,
    "endTime": 306.48,
    "text": "So the seat is not comfortable, it is uncomfortable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.48,
    "endTime": 309.28000000000003,
    "text": "That's how prefixes and suffixes can be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.28,
    "endTime": 311.4,
    "text": "used in English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.4,
    "endTime": 316.88,
    "text": "The second sentence, “She has a black car.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.88,
    "endTime": 319.48,
    "text": "Can you spot the adjective, first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.48,
    "endTime": 322.5,
    "text": "Of course, it's the adjective 'black'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.5,
    "endTime": 326.1,
    "text": "Is there a suffix or a prefix?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.1,
    "endTime": 328.70000000000005,
    "text": "No, there isn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.7,
    "endTime": 334.26,
    "text": "Next sentence.\r\n“His father was unhelpful.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.26,
    "endTime": 337.15999999999997,
    "text": "What's the adjective?\r\n'unhelpful'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.169,
    "endTime": 338.97999999999996,
    "text": "Of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.98,
    "endTime": 342.0,
    "text": "Any prefix, suffix?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.0,
    "endTime": 347.06,
    "text": "Yes, there is a prefix.\r\nAgain, which is 'un'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.07,
    "endTime": 352.319,
    "text": "To make the adjective negative.\r\nAnd there is a suffix, 'ful'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.319,
    "endTime": 356.1,
    "text": "To make the noun 'help' into an adjective."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 356.1,
    "endTime": 358.46000000000004,
    "text": "'unhelpful'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.46,
    "endTime": 363.28,
    "text": "Next sentence.\r\n“The actor is handsome.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.28,
    "endTime": 367.94,
    "text": "The adjective, of course, is 'handsome'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 367.94,
    "endTime": 370.84,
    "text": "Is there a prefix?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 370.84,
    "endTime": 372.09,
    "text": "No, there isn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 372.09,
    "endTime": 374.64,
    "text": "Is there a suffix?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.64,
    "endTime": 377.21999999999997,
    "text": "Of course, 'some'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.22,
    "endTime": 379.52000000000004,
    "text": "'handsome'"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.52,
    "endTime": 383.02,
    "text": "“I hate oily food.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.02,
    "endTime": 387.18,
    "text": "The adjective is 'oily'.\r\nOf course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.18,
    "endTime": 389.48,
    "text": "Is there a prefix?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 389.48,
    "endTime": 390.8,
    "text": "There isn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.2,
    "endTime": 534.589,
    "text": "Is there a suffix?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.589,
    "endTime": 535.7600000000001,
    "text": "Of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.76,
    "endTime": 544.17,
    "text": "The 'y' is a suffix.\r\nYou have the word, the noun, 'oil'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.17,
    "endTime": 554.03,
    "text": "And to make it into an adjective you add the\r\nsuffix 'y'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.03,
    "endTime": 560.769,
    "text": "And finally,\r\n“She is a dishonest woman.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.769,
    "endTime": 569.03,
    "text": "The adjective is 'dishonest', of course."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.03,
    "endTime": 571.579,
    "text": "Do you have a prefix?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.579,
    "endTime": 579.1999999999999,
    "text": "We do. Yes.\r\nWe have the prefix, 'dis'."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.2,
    "endTime": 582.2900000000001,
    "text": "It shows this woman is not honest, she is\r\ndishonest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.29,
    "endTime": 587.05,
    "text": "Okay, so that's how with prefixes and suffixes\r\nwe can really transform words in English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.05,
    "endTime": 591.12,
    "text": "It's wonderful isn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.12,
    "endTime": 599.839,
    "text": "There are thousands of prefixes and suffixes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.839,
    "endTime": 606.36,
    "text": "Again, these are just a few examples.\r\nBut I hope you now understand how it works"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.36,
    "endTime": 609.86,
    "text": "in English and how you can really transform\r\nand play with the different words and kinds"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.86,
    "endTime": 618.8100000000001,
    "text": "of words."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.81,
    "endTime": 624.27,
    "text": "Okay, guys. Let's now review the sentences"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.27,
    "endTime": 630.18,
    "text": "together and focus on pronunciation."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.18,
    "endTime": 634.9899999999999,
    "text": "Repeat after me, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.99,
    "endTime": 647.1,
    "text": "“I have an uncomfortable seat.”\r\n“I have an uncomfortable seat.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.1,
    "endTime": 646.1800000000001,
    "text": "Good job.\r\nSecond sentence."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.18,
    "endTime": 652.3389999999999,
    "text": "“She has a black car.”\r\n“She has a black car.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.339,
    "endTime": 660.149,
    "text": "Good.\r\nKeep repeating."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 660.149,
    "endTime": 664.589,
    "text": "“His father was unhelpful.”\r\n“His father was unhelpful.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.589,
    "endTime": 673.11,
    "text": "“The actor is handsome.”\r\n“The actor is handsome.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.11,
    "endTime": 675.0600000000001,
    "text": "Good.\r\nMoving on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "“I hate oily food.”\r\n“I hate oily food.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "And finally.\r\n“She is a dishonest woman.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.7,
    "endTime": 685.73,
    "text": "“She is a dishonest woman.”"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.73,
    "endTime": 693.72,
    "text": "Excellent guys."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.72,
    "endTime": 696.4200000000001,
    "text": "Okay, guys.\r\nThank you for watching this video."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.42,
    "endTime": 703.2099999999999,
    "text": "I hoped this helped you understand a bit more\r\nabout prefixes and suffixes in English."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.21,
    "endTime": 707.48,
    "text": "Keep practicing.\r\nIt takes practice to get better identifying"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.48,
    "endTime": 712.64,
    "text": "prefixes and suffixes, but I'm sure you\r\ncan do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 712.64,
    "endTime": 717.6999999999999,
    "text": "Make sure you watch the video as I continue\r\ntalking about adjectives in English."
  },
  {
